      "title": "Schools will resume from Monday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education says that government and government-approved private schools will resume on Monday, July 25, 2022.",
        "However, even though schools have started, it is planned to hold schools on Mondays, Tuesdays and Thursdays and engage in learning activities from home on Wednesdays and Fridays."
      ],
